    <h3>Atta (wheat flour)</h3>
    <p>
      Enough for a couple of days of rotis, maybe 250 grams. On Instamart, the smallest size is 1 kilogram at ₹63. The kirana shopkeeper weighs out loose atta on a digital scale to whatever amount the customer asks for. I have a photo of the scale reading exactly 250 grams. The kirana offers a feature Instamart does not have: the user specifies the quantity, and the shop fulfills it.
    </p>

