    </figure>

    <h3>Coffee sachets</h3>
    <p>
      I searched "coffee sachet" on Instamart. The results were instant coffee jars and pouches, none of them sachets. The search even autocorrected the query toward bulk coffee. At the kirana store, Bru sachets hang in strips at ₹2 each. The platform does not just fail to stock sachets — it fails to recognize that sachets are a product category users are searching for.
    </p>

