    </figure>

    <h3>Eggs</h3>
    <p>
      Instamart sells eggs in packs of 6, 10, 12, and 30. The local vendor sells eggs loose — three or four tied in a polyethylene bag. If the household needs five eggs, Instamart's choices are six or ten. The kirana's choice is five.
    </p>

    <figure>
