    </figure>

    <h3>Camphor (karpoora)</h3>
    <p>
      Used daily in Indian households for puja. The kirana sells a ₹1 single-tablet pack. Instamart's smallest is a 40-gram pack at ₹54 to ₹90. For a household that uses one tablet a day, the Instamart pack represents roughly a year's supply purchased in a single transaction.
    </p>

